{"tid":760024,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"年金 技術文","createTime":"2018-07-29T07:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T15:36:43.000Z","uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc62a243ccf298d3f33e55706bc8ad0f29e1f9de","tid":760024,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/@relgitsjg/whoshouldgoforannuity-1db0f3bf3314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40relgitsjg%2Fwhoshouldgoforannuity-1db0f3bf3314&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=96078fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@relgitsjg/whoshouldgoforannuity-1db0f3bf3314</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n有兩類人一定要申請年金，係一定！！<br />\r\n第一類：夫妻皆健在或未離異<br />\r\n－兩人皆65歲以上、75歲下<br />\r\n－兩人身體大致健康<br />\r\n－合共資產不高於$250萬（唔包括自己住緊嘅第一層樓）<br />\r\n－無其他固定收入（如長俸）<br />\r\n－唔介意填多張表拎「長者生活津貼」（簡稱「長生津」）<br />\r\n－名義回報率：7.5&ndash;8.9%（拎20年年金）／9.1&ndash;10.3%（拎30年）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n第二類：個人申請（未婚、婚後離異／其中一方死方）<br />\r\n－65歲以上、75歲下<br />\r\n－身體大致健康<br />\r\n－資產不高於$130萬（唔包括住自己緊嘅第一層樓）<br />\r\n－無其他固定收入（如長俸）<br />\r\n－唔介意填多張表拎「長生津」<br />\r\n－名義回報率：7.1%-9.2%（拎20年年金）／8.7&ndash;10.6%（拎30年）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n重點1. 長生津每年會根據通脹調整。好重要！】<br />\r\n－長生津根據每年通脹調整。假設為3%，長生津將由第1年$2,600上升至第20年嘅$4,696。呢個年金及長生津組合，單人回報更會上升至8.4%（女）／9.1%（女）（20年計）。平均8%嘅回報率，更加吸引！如果你有信心自己好長命，拎到30年，回報率去到10%+！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1 7Q3Tflyao-PSHbVygPBbdg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1600%2F1%207Q3Tflyao-PSHbVygPBbdg.png&h=8c582f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fcfc4b066cef2e81b101f867b828cbaa2c0a34","tid":760024,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ecacb3cb9dc5f13f47f103163fa3caf3a08b57","tid":760024,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"作者咩料子   佢篇文講到好似好易賺錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}